_label: Wedding party, New York Municipal Building Marriage Chambers, waiting room-- second row Simon Pettet poet bridegroom, eternal flower child Rosebud Feliu bride, her son Harley Flanagan of Cro-Mags and his friend Manon Brière, maid of honor with glasses; front row Luc Sante essayist, Maria Saavedra and her fiancé best man Steven Taylor, mid-day, August 1984.
